.Dd August 1, 2006
.Dt SPC 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm spc
.Nd Fujitsu MB87030/MB89352 SCSI driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "spc* at pcmcia? function ?"
.Ss hp300
.Cd "spc0 at dio? scode ?"
.Ss luna68k
.Ss soft68k
.Cd "spc0 at mainbus0"
.Ss x68k
.Cd "spc0 at scsirom0"
.Cd "spc1 at scsirom1"
.Pp
.Cd "scsibus* at spc?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the
.Tn Fujitsu
MB87030/MB89352
.Tn SCSI
Protocol Controller (SPC) chips.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr cd 4 ,
.Xr ch 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pcmcia 4 ,
.Xr scsi 4 ,
.Xr sd 4 ,
.Xr ss 4 ,
.Xr st 4 ,
.Xr uk 4 ,
.Xr scsipi 9
.Sh BUGS
Synchronous data transfers are not currently supported.
